Create Line and clustered Column chart for funded loans by date 16

While creating the line and clustered column chart, choose the visual then drag the repayment interval column to the shared axis, drag the %funded loans measure to the column values and the YOY measure on the line values.

Then go to the format icon and customize your visual with the steps indicated below.

X: 939

Y: 147

W: 660

H: 417

Legend - on, X axis - on,  Y axis -on,  data labels - on, Title -on, tooltip -on,  YOY02 data color - #a8337d, default data color - #70bbff

Title - on, Title background -#0d6abf,   title font - #ffffff,  Title text size -18,  Title alignment - center, Word wrap -ON,  text size -18,  Font family - Segoe Bold, category -off,  border on


On the Y axis set this up ; Text size -14

To set secondary axis  scroll down on the Y-axis  and turn  the Show secondary  -ON , Set secondary axis color - #a8337d




Now create a background for your title as shown below and repeat the step to create the title background for all your visuals, title Background color -#0d6abf
